name: Mesh Chain Maille Bracelet - Handmade in Sterling Silver
description:
HANDMADE AND READY TO SHIP!

This is a handcrafted, one a kind piece of art. A beautiful cuff bracelet made of the finest Sterling Silver. At 9 rows this bracelet is 1.25" wide and 5.75" long that fastens with a sterling silver slide clasp. Intricate and detailed, it took my heart and hard work to produce this, my favorite piece.

This bracelet is flexible and fits fluidly to your wrist. A beautiful accessory that can be worn on any occasion or holiday gathering.

Treat yourself to luxury, or give a hint to your loved one that this will make a perfect gift.
You will receive many compliments from your friends and family on this sparkling piece of jewelry.
